## 2. Package & Dependency Changes

| Item | PF5 | PF6 | Breaking? |
|------|-----|-----|-----------|
| Core package | `@patternfly/react-core@5.x` | `@patternfly/react-core@6.x` | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| Charts package | `@patternfly/react-charts@7.x` | `@patternfly/react-charts@8.x` | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| Table package | `@patternfly/react-table@5.x` | `@patternfly/react-table@6.x` | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| Icons package | `@patternfly/react-icons@5.x` | `@patternfly/react-icons@6.x` | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| Tokens package | `@patternfly/react-tokens@5.x` | `@patternfly/react-tokens@6.x` | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| Victory (charts) | Bundled dependency | **Optional peer dependency** тАФ install `victory` or specific packages like `victory-core`, `victory-tooltip` | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| Deprecated components | `@patternfly/react-core` | `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated` | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| Next components | `@patternfly/react-core/next` | `@patternfly/react-core` (promoted) | тЬЕ BREAKING |

