## 3. CSS Class Prefix Changes

| Item | PF5 | PF6 | Breaking? |
|------|-----|-----|-----------|
| Component classes | `pf-v5-c-*` | `pf-v6-c-*` | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| Layout classes | `pf-v5-l-*` | `pf-v6-l-*` | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| Utility classes | `pf-v5-u-*` | `pf-v6-u-*` | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| Modifier classes | `pf-v5-m-*` stays as `pf-m-*` | Same pattern | тАФ |
| OUIA attributes | `data-ouia-component-type="PF5/*"` | `data-ouia-component-type="PF6/*"` | тЬЕ BREAKING |

**Codemod**: `class-name-updater --v6 --fix` handles this automatically.

