## 4. Design Token / CSS Variable Migration

### 4.1 Variable Naming Convention Change

| Item | PF5 | PF6 | Breaking? |
|------|-----|-----|-----------|
| Global variable prefix | `--pf-v5-global--*` | `--pf-t--global--*` | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| Component variable prefix | `--pf-v5-c-*` | `--pf-v6-c-*` | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| React token prefix (global tokens) | `global_*` | `t_global_*` | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| React token prefix (color tokens) | `global_Color_*` | `t_color_*` | тЬЕ BREAKING |

### 4.2 Specific Token Examples

| PF5 CSS Variable | PF6 CSS Variable | Auto-fixable? |
|-----------------|-----------------|---------------|
| `--pf-v5-global--FontSize--lg` | `--pf-t--global--font--size--lg` | тЬЕ Yes |
| `--pf-v5-global--BorderWidth--lg` | `--pf-t--global--border--width--extra-strong` | тЬЕ Yes |
| `--pf-v5-global--BoxShadow--sm` | `--pf-t--global--box-shadow--sm` | тЬЕ Yes |
| `--pf-v5-global--spacer--3xl` | `--pf-t--global--spacer--3xl` | тЬЕ Yes |
| `--pf-v5-global--ZIndex--lg` | `--pf-t--global--z-index--lg` | тЬЕ Yes |
| `--pf-v5-global--Color--100` | `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd` (hot pink placeholder) | тЭМ Manual |
| `--pf-v5-global--Color--200` | `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd` (hot pink placeholder) | тЭМ Manual |
| All component-level tokens (`--pf-v5-c-*`) | Must be found manually | тЭМ Manual |

### 4.3 React Token Examples

| PF5 React Token | PF6 React Token | Auto-fixable? |
|----------------|----------------|---------------|
| `global_FontSize_lg` | `t_global_font_size_lg` | тЬЕ Yes |
| `global_FontWeight_normal` | `global_font_weight_body_default` | тЬЕ Yes |
| `global_Color_100` | `t_temp_dev_tbd` (must be manually replaced) | тЭМ Manual |
| `global_link_Color_hover` | Find equivalent in PF6 token docs | тЭМ Manual |
| `color_green_10` | `t_color_green_10` | тЬЕ Yes |
| Component tokens (`c_badge_PaddingLeft`, etc.) | No auto-fix available | тЭМ Manual |

