## 5. Breakpoint Changes

| Breakpoint | PF5 (pixels) | PF6 Token | PF6 (rems) | Breaking? |
|-----------|-------------|-----------|-----------|-----------|
| xs | 0px | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--xs` | 0rem | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| sm | 576px | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--sm` | 36rem | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| md | 768px | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--md` | 48rem | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| lg | 992px | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--lg` | 62rem | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| xl | 1200px | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--xl` | 75rem | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| 2xl | 1450px | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--2xl` | 90.625rem | тЬЕ BREAKING |

> **Action**: Any hardcoded pixel breakpoint logic must be converted to rem (divide px by 16).

