## 6. Component Migration - Removed/Deprecated

### 6.1 Fully Removed Components (no fix, must rewrite)

| Component | Replacement | Breaking? |
|-----------|-------------|-----------|
| **Application Launcher** (deprecated) | Custom menu with Menu/MenuToggle | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| **Context Selector** (deprecated) | Custom menu with Menu/MenuToggle | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| **Dropdown** (old deprecated) | New composable Dropdown or Dropdown template | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| **Options Menu** (deprecated) | Composable Select or Select template | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| **Page Header** (deprecated) | Masthead + Toolbar | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| **Select** (old deprecated) | New composable Select or Select template | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| **KebabToggle** | `<MenuToggle variant="plain" icon={<EllipsisVIcon />} />` | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| **PageNavigation** | Removed entirely; use PageSection | тЬЕ BREAKING |

### 6.2 Deprecated (moved to `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated`)

| Component | Status | Recommended Replacement |
|-----------|--------|------------------------|
| **Chip / ChipGroup** | Deprecated тЖТ `react-core/deprecated` | Use **Label / LabelGroup** with `variant="outline"` |
| **Tile** | Deprecated тЖТ `react-core/deprecated` | Use **Card** (new Tile-like Card example) |
| **DragDrop / Droppable / Draggable** | Deprecated тЖТ `react-core/deprecated` | Use **DragDropSort** from `@patternfly/react-drag-drop` |
| **Modal** (old implementation) | Deprecated тЖТ `react-core/deprecated` | Use new **Modal** (promoted from `react-core/next`) |
| **DualListSelector** (old) | Deprecated тЖТ `react-core/deprecated` | Use new **DualListSelector** (promoted from `react-core/next`) |

### 6.3 Promoted from `/next` to main

| Component | PF5 Import | PF6 Import |
|-----------|-----------|-----------|
| **Modal** | `@patternfly/react-core/next` | `@patternfly/react-core` |
| **DualListSelector** | `@patternfly/react-core/next` | `@patternfly/react-core` |

