## 8. Component Migration - Prop Changes

### 8.1 EmptyState (Major Refactoring)

| Change | PF5 | PF6 | Auto-fixable? | Breaking? |
|--------|-----|-----|---------------|-----------|
| Header moved into EmptyState | `<EmptyState><EmptyStateHeader titleText="..." icon={<EmptyStateIcon icon={Icon} />} /></EmptyState>` | `<EmptyState titleText="..." icon={Icon} headingLevel="h4">` | тЪая╕П Partial | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| EmptyStateHeader | Separate component | **No longer exported** тАФ props moved to EmptyState | тЪая╕П Partial | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| EmptyStateIcon | Separate component | **No longer exported** тАФ pass icon directly to EmptyState's `icon` prop | тЪая╕П Partial | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| headerClassName | `<EmptyStateHeader className="...">` | `<EmptyState headerClassName="...">` | тЬЕ Yes | тЬЕ BREAKING |

### 8.2 Button

| Change | PF5 | PF6 | Auto-fixable? | Breaking? |
|--------|-----|-----|---------------|-----------|
| `isActive` renamed | `<Button isActive />` | `<Button isClicked />` | тЬЕ Yes | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| Icons must use `icon` prop | `<Button variant="plain"><SomeIcon /></Button>` | `<Button variant="plain" icon={<SomeIcon />} />` | тЬЕ Yes | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| `isDisabled` behavior | Sets `aria-disabled` | Now sets `disabled` attr; `aria-disabled` only when `component` is not "button" | тЪая╕П Manual | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| Text wrapper | Direct text children | Wrapping `<span>` around text (affects `byText` queries) | тЭМ Manual | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| `isFavorite`/`isFavorited` | Use `<StarIcon>` as children | `<Button isFavorite={true} />` | тЬЕ Yes | Optional |
| `isHamburgerButton` | `<PageToggleButton><BarsIcon /></PageToggleButton>` | `<PageToggleButton isHamburgerButton />` | тЬЕ Yes | Optional |

