| All "chip" prop names renamed | `chips`, `deleteChipGroup`, `deleteChip`, `chipGroupExpandedText`, `chipGroupCollapsedText`, `expandableChipContainerRef`, `chipContainerRef`, `chipGroupContentRef`, `customChipGroupContent` | `labels`, `deleteLabelGroup`, `deleteLabel`, `labelGroupExpandedText`, `labelGroupCollapsedText`, `expandableLabelContainerRef`, `labelContainerRef`, `labelGroupContentRef`, `customLabelGroupContent` | тЬЕ Yes | тЬЕ BREAKING |

