| `isPlainButtonAction` removed | `<DataListAction isPlainButtonAction />` | `<DataListAction />` | тЬЕ Yes | тЬЕ BREAKING |

### 8.27 JumpLinksItem

| Change | PF5 | PF6 | Auto-fixable? | Breaking? |
