## 9. Charts Migration

| Change | PF5 | PF6 | Auto-fixable? | Breaking? |
|--------|-----|-----|---------------|-----------|
| Import path changed | `import { Chart } from '@patternfly/react-charts'` | `import { Chart } from '@patternfly/react-charts/victory'` | тЬЕ Yes | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| Victory dependency | Bundled | **Optional peer dependency** тАФ must install separately | тЭМ Manual (npm install) | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| Victory installation | Automatic | `npm install victory` OR install specific: `victory-core`, `victory-tooltip`, etc. | тЭМ Manual | тЬЕ BREAKING |

> **Note**: This change enables future support for multiple chart libraries. All Victory-based chart components (Chart, ChartArea, ChartBar, ChartDonut, etc.) must use the `/victory` sub-path.

---

## 10. Icon Changes

| Change | PF5 | PF6 | Auto-fixable? | Breaking? |
|--------|-----|-----|---------------|-----------|
| Icons in Button | Passed as children | Must use `icon` prop for `variant="plain"` buttons | тЬЕ Yes | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| Icons in NavItem | Passed as children alongside links | Use `icon` prop on NavItem | тЭМ Manual | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| Icons in MenuToggle | Passed as children for plain variant | Use `icon` prop | тЭМ Manual | тЬЕ BREAKING |
| BarsIcon in PageToggleButton | `<PageToggleButton><BarsIcon /></PageToggleButton>` | `<PageToggleButton isHamburgerButton />` | тЬЕ Yes | Optional |
| StarIcon in Button | `<Button><StarIcon /></Button>` | `<Button isFavorite={true} />` | тЬЕ Yes | Optional |
| EmptyStateIcon | Separate wrapping component | Removed; pass icon directly to `<EmptyState icon={CubesIcon}>` | тЪая╕П Partial | тЬЕ BREAKING |

---

## 11. Layout Changes

### Flex / FlexItem

No explicit breaking prop changes were documented in the PF5тЖТPF6 codemods for Flex/FlexItem. However:

| Change | Details | Breaking? |
|--------|---------|-----------|
| CSS class prefix | `pf-v5-l-flex` тЖТ `pf-v6-l-flex` | тЬЕ BREAKING (handled by class-name-updater) |
| CSS variables | All `--pf-v5-l-flex--*` variables renamed to `--pf-v6-l-flex--*` or token equivalents | тЬЕ BREAKING |

### Other Layouts

All layout CSS classes (`Bullseye`, `Gallery`, `Grid`, `Level`, `Split`, `Stack`) have the `pf-v5` тЖТ `pf-v6` prefix change.

---

## 12. Testing Impact

### 12.1 Button Test Failures

| Issue | Cause | Fix |
|-------|-------|-----|
| Cannot find `aria-disabled` | `isDisabled` now sets `disabled` attr, not `aria-disabled` | Remove tests checking `aria-disabled` on native buttons |
| Cannot find button attrs with `byText` | New wrapping `<span>` around button text | Use `byRole('button', { name: '...' })` instead of `byText` |

### 12.2 Select Test Failures

| Issue | Cause | Fix |
|-------|-------|-----|
| Cannot find role (RTL) | Popper menu `aria-disabled` after selection | Pass `{ hidden: true }` option or set `appendTo="inline"` |

### 12.3 General Test Impact

| Area | Details |
|------|---------|
| OUIA selectors | `PF5/` тЖТ `PF6/` in `data-ouia-component-type` |
| CSS class selectors | `pf-v5-` тЖТ `pf-v6-` everywhere |
| Snapshot tests | Will break due to class name changes, structural changes |
| `pf-m-selectable` | Removed from TreeView list items |
| Sticky cell CSS vars | `--pf-v6-c-table__sticky-cell--Left` тЖТ `--pf-v6-c-table__sticky-cell--InsetInlineStart` |
| Slider step CSS vars | `--pf-v6-c-slider__step--Left` тЖТ `--pf-v6-c-slider__step--InsetInlineStart` |

### 12.4 Markup Changes (may affect selectors/tests)

These components have **internal markup changes** that could break CSS selectors or test queries:

- AccordionItem (new `div` wrapper)
- Button (new `span` around text, icon wrapper changes)
- DrawerHead (no longer renders DrawerPanelBody internally)
- JumpLinksItem (uses Button internally)
- LoginMainHeader (uses `div` instead of `header`)
- MenuItemAction (uses Button internally)
- Masthead structure (MastheadToggle inside MastheadMain)
- NotificationBadge (uses stateful button)
- NotificationDrawerHeader (native `h1` instead of Text)
- Page (PageBody wrapper behavior)
- Pagination (wrapper around PaginationOptionsMenu toggle)
- SliderStep (CSS variable rename)
- Tabs scroll buttons (Button components + wrapper div)
- Th/Td sticky cells (CSS variable rename)
- Toolbar/ToolbarLabelGroupContent
- WizardFooter (uses ActionList)
- WizardNavItem (wrapper around content)

---

## Summary Statistics

| Category | Count |
|----------|-------|
| Fully removed components | 8 |
| Deprecated тЖТ `/deprecated` | 5 |
