| Components with removed props | ~25 |
| Components with renamed props | ~20 |
| Components with structural/markup changes | ~20 |
| CSS token/variable changes | Thousands (new token system) |
| Codemod tools available | 4 |
| Auto-fixable changes | ~70% |
| Manual-only changes | ~30% |

---

## Quick Reference: Most Common Migration Actions

1. **Run codemods first** тАФ handles ~70% of changes automatically
2. **Update all imports** тАФ deprecated components move to `/deprecated`, `/next` components promoted
3. **Charts**: Change import path to `@patternfly/react-charts/victory`, install `victory` peer dep
4. **EmptyState**: Major refactoring тАФ `EmptyStateHeader` and `EmptyStateIcon` absorbed into `EmptyState`
5. **Text тЖТ Content**: All Text/TextContent/TextList/TextListItem тЖТ Content with `component` prop
6. **Chip тЖТ Label**: Replace Chip/ChipGroup with Label/LabelGroup (`variant="outline"`)
7. **CSS classes**: `pf-v5-*` тЖТ `pf-v6-*` everywhere
8. **CSS variables**: `--pf-v5-global--*` тЖТ `--pf-t--global--*` (new token system)
9. **React tokens**: `global_*` тЖТ `t_global_*`; color tokens тЖТ `t_temp_dev_tbd` (manual replacement needed)
10. **Breakpoints**: Pixel values тЖТ rem values
11. **Button**: `isActive` тЖТ `isClicked`, icons must use `icon` prop
12. **Remove CSS overrides** тАФ old overrides will target non-existent variables



