    <li><strong>Build parity:</strong> Both branches build successfully with the same 7 pre-existing TypeScript errors тАФ no regressions from either migration.</li>
    <li><strong>Scope:</strong> Branch 2 has minor scope creep (1 test timestamp fix, 1 rename) but these are trivial. Branch 1 has significant whitespace churn (tabsтЖТspaces) adding noise to a small diff.</li>
