<!-- 6.2 EmptyState -->
<a id="det-emptystate"></a>
<details open>
  <summary>6.2 EmptyState Migration <span class="badge badge-red" style="margin-left:8px">Critical Gap on B1</span></summary>
  <div class="detail-body">
    <h4>What changed in PF6</h4>
    <p>EmptyState underwent major refactoring in PF6:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><code>EmptyStateHeader</code> and <code>EmptyStateIcon</code> are <strong>no longer separate components</strong></li>
      <li><code>titleText</code> should be a <strong>plain string</strong> (not a <code>&lt;Title&gt;</code> element), with <code>headingLevel</code> as a separate prop</li>
      <li><code>icon</code> prop takes the icon directly (as element in some cases, component in others)</li>
      <li><code>EmptyStateFooter</code> and <code>EmptyStateActions</code> wrap buttons</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>PF6 Correct Pattern</h4>
    <pre><code>&lt;EmptyState
  titleText="My Title"
  headingLevel="h4"
  icon={MyIcon}
  variant={EmptyStateVariant.sm}
&gt;
  &lt;EmptyStateBody&gt;...&lt;/EmptyStateBody&gt;
  &lt;EmptyStateFooter&gt;
    &lt;EmptyStateActions&gt;...&lt;/EmptyStateActions&gt;
  &lt;/EmptyStateFooter&gt;
&lt;/EmptyState&gt;</code></pre>

    <h4>Branch Comparison</h4>
    <table>
      <tr><th>File</th><th>pf-codemods</th><th>semver/goose</th></tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>dashboard-list.tsx</code></td>
        <td><span class="cross">тЬЧ</span> <strong>Incorrect:</strong> <code>titleText={&lt;Title headingLevel="h4" size="lg"&gt;...&lt;/Title&gt;}</code> тАФ wraps in <code>&lt;Title&gt;</code> element which is wrong for PF6</td>
        <td><span class="check">тЬУ</span> Correct: <code>titleText={&lt;span data-test="..."&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;}</code> with <code>headingLevel="h4"</code>; <code>&lt;EmptyStateFooter&gt;</code>/<code>&lt;EmptyStateActions&gt;</code> added</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>DashboardEmptyState.tsx</code></td>
        <td><span class="cross">тЬЧ</span> <strong>Not touched:</strong> Still uses <code>titleText={&lt;Title headingLevel="h2" size="lg"&gt;}</code></td>
        <td><span class="check">тЬУ</span> Correct: <code>titleText={t('...')}</code> as plain string, <code>headingLevel="h2"</code></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>ProjectEmptyState.tsx</code></td>
        <td><span class="cross">тЬЧ</span> <strong>Not touched:</strong> Still uses <code>&lt;Title&gt;</code> wrapper</td>
        <td><span class="check">тЬУ</span> Correct: plain string <code>titleText</code>, <code>headingLevel="h2"</code></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>query-browser.tsx</code></td>
        <td><span class="cross">тЬЧ</span> <strong>Not touched:</strong> Still uses <code>&lt;Title&gt;</code> wrapper</td>
        <td><span class="check">тЬУ</span> Correct: <code>titleText={title}</code> as string, <code>headingLevel="h2"</code></td>
      </tr>
